	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Block commenting was one of them. I also hated how with NESASM you had to have a symbol to force zero-page addressing so I did away with that.
<br />
<br /> I was/am also working on an optimization tool that recommends possible areas to work on (assuming you enable the feature).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
